## Project Overview
Complete lifecycle template for AI-powered web application development, from concept to production and ongoing support.

## Project Type
AI

## Project Stages
📑 Defined - AI Web App Development Template
📆 Planned - Requirements gathering, tech stack selection, AI model evaluation
▶️ In progress - Development phases (PoC → MVP → Production)
